There is an exam on the rules of the road. The Examiner:
- Crossroads, here you are, here a bus, here a truck, here a motorcycle. Who will pass first?
The examinee:
- The taxi driver.
The Examiner:
- Why the taxi driver? Which taxi driver? Where did the taxi driver come from?
The examinee:
- Fuck knows where these taxi drivers come from all the time.
